Title: Supernova
Writer: William Malone (story), Daniel Chuba (story), David C. Wilson (screenplay)
Actors: James Spader, Angela Bassett, Robert Forster, Lou Diamond Phillips
Plot: A deep space rescue and recovery spaceship with a crew of 6 receives a distress call from a mining operation 3432 light years away. A rescue operation via dimension jump is made. Bad idea.
Production: Screenland Pictures, United Artists, Hammerhead Productions, Metro Goldwyn Mayer
